âš™ï¸ SECTION 2: Model Settings â€” The â€œDialsâ€ You Must Control
These settings are NOT optional. They dramatically change output quality.

1. ğŸŒ¡ï¸ Temperature â€” The â€œCreativity Knobâ€
What it does: Controls randomness in word selection.
How it works:
Low temp (0.0â€“0.3) â†’ AI plays it safe â†’ chooses most probable word â†’ great for facts, code, math.
High temp (0.7â€“1.0+) â†’ AI gets wild â†’ picks surprising words â†’ great for stories, jokes, brainstorming.
Temp = 0 â†’ â€œGreedy decodingâ€ â†’ always picks #1 most likely word â†’ deterministic (same input = same output).
Temp > 1 â†’ Chaos mode â†’ all words become equally likely â†’ often leads to nonsense or loops.
ğŸ’¡ Pro Tip: For ANY task requiring accuracy (math, classification, code) â†’ ALWAYS set Temperature = 0. 

2. ğŸ” Top-K & Top-P â€” The â€œIdea Filtersâ€
These limit which words the AI can choose from.

â¤ Top-K (e.g., K=20)
Only considers the top 20 most likely next words.
Low K (1â€“10) â†’ Focused, factual.
High K (50â€“100) â†’ Creative, varied.
K=1 â†’ Same as greedy (Temp=0).
â¤ Top-P (a.k.a. Nucleus Sampling, e.g., P=0.9)
Considers enough top words until their combined probability â‰¥ 90%.
Low P (0.1â€“0.5) â†’ Very focused.
High P (0.9â€“1.0) â†’ Very open-ended.
ğŸ’¡ Pro Tip: Use Top-P = 0.95 and Top-K = 30 as your default starting point. Adjust from there. 

3. ğŸ“ Max Tokens â€” The â€œAnswer Length Limiterâ€
Sets maximum number of tokens (words/pieces) in the response.
More tokens = slower, more expensive, higher chance of rambling.
Important: AI doesnâ€™t â€œtry to be shortâ€ â€” it just gets cut off. So ALSO say in your prompt: â€œAnswer in 1 sentence.â€
4. ğŸ”„ Sampling Interaction â€” How Settings Work Together
If you use Temp + Top-K + Top-P â†’ AI first filters words using K & P â†’ then applies Temp to pick from that filtered list.
If Temp = 0 â†’ Top-K & Top-P are IGNORED â†’ always picks #1 word.
If Top-K = 1 â†’ Temp & Top-P are IGNORED.
If Top-P = 0 â†’ Only #1 word considered â†’ same as greedy.
ğŸš¨ WARNING: High Temp + High Top-K/P â†’ Risk of â€œRepetition Loop Bugâ€ â†’ AI gets stuck saying â€œ...and then... and then... and then...â€ 

